#. ~ Description for Necropolis Actually Findable
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Tired of all that futile search for Necropolis? Sick after checking "
"5165846512354 overmaps to no avail? Worry no more, this mod solves that "
"problem! It makes Necropolis findable by making it spawn in a similar way "
"the refugee center does - exactly once per overmap."
msgstr ""
